-| ARM            | MMU-600         | #1076982        | N/A                         |
+| ARM            | MMU-600         | #1076982,1209401| N/A                         |
 +----------------+-----------------+-----------------+-----------------------------+
-| ARM            | MMU-700         | #2812531        | N/A                         |
+| ARM            | MMU-700         | #2268618,2812531| N/A                         |
 +----------------+-----------------+-----------------+-----------------------------+
